*mysqltool-0.95 (17 Apr 2002)

  17 Apr 2002; Donny Davies <woodchip@gentoo.org> :
  Created an ebuild for mysqltool, a perl-based frontend for administering
  MySQL servers.  Similiar to phpMyAdmin.
